targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  time,
  latitude,
  horizontal_accuracy_m
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND latitude IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT
  time,
  latitude,
  longitude
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND latitude IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT
  time,
  latitude,
  longitude,
  ground_heading_deg * 100000 AS ground_heading_deg
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time)
ORDER BY
  time DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT
  time,
  altitude_m,
  altitude_m + vertical_accuracy_m AS upper_bound,
  altitude_m - vertical_accuracy_m AS lower_bound
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND latitude IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT
  time,
  ground_speed_ms,
  ground_speed_ms + speed_accuracy_ms AS upper_bound,
  GREATEST(ground_speed_ms - speed_accuracy_ms, 0) AS lower_bound
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND latitude IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT
  fix_ok_int
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND fix_ok_int IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT
  fix_type_int
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND fix_type_int IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT
  ntrip_client_rtcm_recieved_int
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND ntrip_client_rtcm_recieved_int IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT
  carrier_phase_range_int
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time) AND carrier_phase_range_int IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
  time

SELECT
  time,
  latitude,
  longitude,
  ground_heading_deg * 100000 AS ground_heading_deg
FROM
  metrics
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(time)
ORDER BY
  time DESC
LIMIT 1
